{"data":[{"date":"17:18 26/06","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft sau khi \"g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c\" cho tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/cau-thu-thuy-dien-bi-doa-giet-sau-khi-gop-suc-cho-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3831","checkdouble":"189640"},{"date":"17:24 26/06","title":"Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb C\u0110V nh\u00e0 s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/salah-va-cac-dong-doi-bi-cdv-nha-si-nhuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Volgograd gi\u1eefa ti\u1ebfng la \u00f3, sau tr\u1eadn thua \u1ea2-r\u1eadp X\u00ea-\u00fat v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2 h\u00f4m qua 25/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n xe bu\u00fdt \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfng ch\u1eedi: \"L\u0169 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t\". Ti\u1ebfng h\u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi chi\u1ebfc xe khu\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c b\u1edfi C\u0110V nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn thua Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c b\u1edfi C\u0110V nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn thua Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/salah-3865-1529998526.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c th\u1eadm t\u1ec7. \u1ea2nh: AP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n bu\u1ed3n phi\u1ec1n. T\u1eeb t\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1y l\u00f2ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd ABS-CBN, h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng chuy\u00ean c\u01a1. T\u1edd Egypt Independent \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh 10.000 C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Salah v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c, khi gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thua c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn \u1edf Nga, ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ec1u do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Salah. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 \u1ea2-r\u1eadp X\u00ea-\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chuyen-gia-bong-da-dot-tu-vi-that-bai-cua-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189598.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap-469-189567.html\">Salah nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-461-189549.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-421-189538.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3830","checkdouble":"189641"},{"date":"13:46 26/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Thanh H\u00f3a 0-0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng (H2): B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng su\u00fdt b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/thanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/web