ype":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL\u00a0Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP HAGL VS QU\u1ea2NG NINH</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3828","checkdouble":"189604"},{"date":"16:31 26/06","title":"Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alex Sandro cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/juventus-chot-gia-ban-alex-sandro-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Juventus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/juventus-chot-gia-ban-alex-sandro-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Young, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-vi-tri-hau-ve-trai-172-182680.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n Mua Sandro</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Chelsea c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i, song M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Sandro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro\" title=\"Alex Sandro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alex Sandro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi&nbsp;l\u1edbn h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, M.U d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Juventus \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, M.U s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Juventus, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-mua-jose-gaya-cua-valencia-172-182126.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n sang Jose Gaya c\u1ee7a Valencia</span> thay v\u00ec b\u1ecf ra 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3827","checkdouble":"189632"},{"date":"17:00 26/06","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Brighton n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger t\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Brighton.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 ra s\u00e2n trong c\u1ea3 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Brighton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewis Dunk c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Laurent Koscielny.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emrates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/dunk.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk v\u00ec Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lewis Dunk, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-tra-gia-dat-koscielny-chan-thuong-nang-mat-world-cup-184-185546.html\" target=\"_blank\">Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 12 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mustafi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Chambers hay Holding, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1ecd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3826","checkdouble":"189633"},{"date":"11:07 26/06","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/chuyen-gia-bong-da-dot-tu-vi-that-bai-cua-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a CLB Zalamek, \u00f4ng Abdel Rahim Mohamed \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi ngay sau khi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua Saudi Arabia \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u00ean Ai C\u1eadp b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hector Cuper t\u1ea1i Nga \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn cho NHM x\u1ee9 s\u1edf kim t\u1ef1 th\u00e1p. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y x\u1ea5u. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/180626_091633_76.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, \u00f4ng Abdel Rahim Mohamed, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a CLB Zalamek, \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi ngay sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng Abdel Rahim Mohamed hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh qu\u1ed1c gia Ai C\u1eadp. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y do r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u00ean, \u00f4ng Mohamed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c con trai l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a t\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Hector Cuper \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Mohamed.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap-469-189567.html\">Salah nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-463-189530.html\">Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp (KT): Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Saudi Arabia ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-461-189549.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3825","checkdouble":"189598"},{"date":"09:55 26/06","title":"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\" v\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Verratti</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Hy-sinh-Pogba,-MU-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-bang-duoc-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Verratti\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Marco Verratti c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u00fat xa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede H\u00e8 2017, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Barca \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 khi Barca ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro trong khi PSG \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t Verratti, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-mua-verratti-voi-gia-75-trieu-bang-172-187639.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU san sang doi Pogba lay Verratti\" title=\"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi 2 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVerratti d\u00f9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi M.U, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Pogba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3824","checkdouble":"189590"},{"date":"11:02 26/06","title":"Chelsea ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chia tay Napoli c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-thang-7-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Express, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t n\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Conte, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, \u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Express c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n mua c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng Sarri c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n David Luiz l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Daniele Rugani v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u00a0\u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i HLV Sarri c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Morata v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh ngay\u00a0H\u00e8 2018. Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3823","checkdouble":"189593"},{"date":"08:32 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/8/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-than-quang-ninh-18h00-ngay-266-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB HAGL v\u1eeba t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15 v\u1eeba qua.Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh?</h2><h2>HAGL \u2013 ch\u1ee7 kh\u00e1t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap HAGL c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 26/6.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 266) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 266) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-HAGL-vs-Than-Quang-Ninh-(18h00-ngay-266)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nguy c\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n HAGL m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng G\u1ed7 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec may ra h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0 b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecf xa tr\u00ean BXH. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecf xa v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch\u2026 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-4 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00f4m 13/6 v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2/6 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ho\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Sanna Kh\u00e1nh Ho\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nho\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f2n \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf m\u1ed7i chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch trong 6 tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa qu\u00ea, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i Pleiku l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 HAGL \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/truc-tiep-quang-ninh-vs-hagl-18h00-ngay-96-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 5-0 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u00fap QG. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c hi v\u1ecdng th\u00eam v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a HAGL, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 Osmar. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng SLNA, nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ninh v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho s\u00e2n Pleiku hi v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean G\u1ed7 s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t 3 n\u1ed9i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00ec th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, HAGL \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 26 l\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi G\u1ed7 trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u01b0ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, HAGL may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i nay 26/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 tr\u1eadn, HAGL th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 5.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HAGL, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL:\u00a0V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn; \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u, Anh T\u00e0i, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Osmar, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh:\u00a0Tu\u1ea5n Linh; Thanh H\u00e0o, Thanh Hi\u1ec1n, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Vi\u1ebft Tri\u1ec1u, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, H\u1ea3i Huy, Nh\u1eadt Minh, Eydison, H\u1ed3ng Qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3822","checkdouble":"189584"},{"date":"21:09 25/06","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 16 V-League: Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch ch\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/truoc-vong-16-vleague-thu-thach-cho-ha-noi-va-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 16 V-League ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Trong khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam th\u00ec HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eebng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 12, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111ang k\u00e9m H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 16 V-League Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch ch\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 16 V-League Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch ch\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Truoc-vong-16-V-League-Thu-thach-cho-Ha-Noi-va-HAGL-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110</em><em>\u00a0Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 th\u00ec trong 14 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 th\u1eafng 12 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng lu\u00f4n \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i khi ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00ean Gia Lai, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 vay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HAGL c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ch\u00e2u Ng\u1ecdc Quang \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch trong khi Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh Motta m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap cho \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/cong-phuong-lap-sieu-pham-hagl-van-thua-dau-phut-cuoi-700x366-0052.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL\u00a0<em>\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn, V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a VFF. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Do v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng sau c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o v\u00e0 Diego Fagan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang ch\u00ecm trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, c\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG l\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. D\u00f9 V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0110TQG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>SLNA vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p SLNA, CLB \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n To\u00e0n Em s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng l\u00fan s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua tr\u00ean BXH. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n 1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 d\u1ec5 khi m\u00e0 SLNA th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0? Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i mai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i 4 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean, 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15 V-League l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u2013 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, TP.HCM \u2013 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u2013 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 26/6. Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"LTD vong 16 V-League 2018\" title=\"LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/210719-Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3821","checkdouble":"189552"},{"date":"18:17 25/06","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Roma","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/24/pastore-tien-gan-roma.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Javier Pastore s\u1ebd bay \u0111\u1ebfn Italia trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1edbi Roma.</h2><h2>Pastore ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Roma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-tottenham-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn-172-178766.html\" target=\"_blank\">Javier Pastore \u0111ang t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Paris Saint-Germain</span> h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t 14 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 v\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 West Ham c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Man United c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9 l\u1ed9. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Pastore s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi Roma \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pastore v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pastore v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/24/pastore-tien-gan-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pastore v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palermo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 ho\u1eb7c 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 4 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPastore gia nh\u1eadp PSG t\u1eeb Palermo n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 270 l\u1ea7n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roma ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pastore l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Justin Kluivert t\u1eeb Ajax v\u00e0 Ante Coric t\u1eeb Dinamo Zagreb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Eusebio Di Francesco \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, k\u00e9m nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Juventus 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Roma c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n trung v\u1ec7 18 tu\u1ed5i William Bianda. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Lens t\u1ea1i Ligue 2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-gaya-thay-young-172-189434.html\">M.U t\u00ednh chi 30 tri\u1ec7u cho truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ashley Young</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-milinkovicsavic-va-dung-chieu-doc-172-189490.html\">M.U c\u1eed \u0111i\u1ec7p vi\u00ean th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sao s\u00e1ng Serbia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3820","checkdouble":"189531"},{"date":"19:39 25/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng, Bayern v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 sao cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/28/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-256-nhan-de-nghi-khung-bayern-van-khong-nha-sao-cho-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng, Bayern v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 sao cho Real. </strong>Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Real Madrid nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ed5i Robert Lewandowski l\u1ea5y Karim Benzema. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i song Bayern t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 256 Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewy cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 256 Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewy cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-256-Bayern-khong-ban-Lewy-cho-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski t\u1eeb Bayern</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Juventus \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi Golovin. </strong>\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Aleksandr Golovin, Juventus mu\u1ed1n chi 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nga. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u1eadt s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juve kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Wilshere, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nDortmund lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua Morata. </strong>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Borussia Dortmund, Michael Zorc kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra cho Morata l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 cao b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thay th\u1ebf cho Pierre Emerick Aubameyang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Pastore s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Roma gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</strong> Javier Pastore s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Italia v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi AS Roma. Sau ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Paris Saint-Germain, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Liverpool, West Ham \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Pastore\" title=\"tien ve Pastore\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/4/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-0711-Depay-tu-choi-roi-MU-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pastore s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u00ea Hazard ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.</strong> Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Chelsea d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t song ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Carragher: \"\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\".</strong> \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m qua sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Panama v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-1 t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod. Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9. </strong>Trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018. Anh cho hay t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Lukaku r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3819","checkdouble":"189544"}]}